_data.text:
The package adds an app layout with a beautiful sidebar styled with tailwindcss. ## Livewire layout The application layout is located in `resources/views/layouts`. It use different components: - Sidebar (`x-jet-bar-sidebar`). - Navigation Menu (`x-jet-bar-navigation-menu`). - Navigation Menu / Responsive links (`x-jet-bar-responsive-links`). There you can add any link or customize it as you need. Navigation menu component ships with a notifications dropdown element, feel free to use or discard it as your app needs. ## InertiaJS layout The application layout is located in `resources/js/Layouts`. It use different components: - Sidebar (`jet-bar-sidebar`). - Navigation Menu (`jet-navigation-menu`). - Navigation Menu / Responsive links (`jet-bar-responsive-links`). There you can add any link or customize it as you need. ## App layout slots it adds two slots: - Header (It adds optionally a `

` tag title to the current page). - Default slot (where it adds all the content).

_data.title: Setup
_data.text:
## Installation

Add `jetbar` using composer:

<code-group>
  <code-block label="composer" active>

  ```bash[terminal/cmd]
  composer require arielmejiadev/jetbar --dev
  ```

  </code-block>
</code-group>

## Install the components

<code-group>
  <code-block label="For Livewire stack" active>

  ```php[terminal/cmd]
  php artisan jetbar:install 
  ```

  </code-block>
  <code-block label="For InertiaJS stack">

  ```php[terminal/cmd]
  php artisan jetbar:install --inertia
  ```

  </code-block>
</code-group>

_data.text:
Este paquete agrega un layout con un hermoso sidebar como layout de tu applicacin estilizado con tailwindcss. ## Plantilla con Livewire La plantilla se encuentra en: `resources/views/layouts`. Este usa los siguientes componentes: - Sidebar (`x-jet-bar-sidebar`). - Navigation Menu (`x-jet-navigation-menu`). - Navigation Menu / Responsive links (`x-jet-bar-responsive-links`). Ah puedes agregar links o personalizar tu plantilla como requieras. El componente Navigation menu agrega un dropdown para notificaciones del usuario, puedes usar o descartar este elemento segn haga sentido en tu app. ## Plantilla con InertiaJS La plantilla se encuentra en: `resources/js/Layouts`. Este usa los siguientes componentes: - Sidebar (`jet-bar-sidebar`). - Navigation Menu (`jet-navigation-menu`). - Navigation Menu / Responsive links (`jet-bar-responsive-links`). Ah puedes agregar links o personalizar tu plantilla como requieras. ## App layout slots Ambos layouts tienen dos `slots` - Header (Agrega opcionalmente un titulo con el tag `

` en la pagina actual). - Default slot (Donde se agrega todo el contenido).
